com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns

Class EmailCampaignRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.constantcontact.components.Component
      • com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.EmailCampaignBase
        • com.constantcontact.components.emailcampaigns.EmailCampaignRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class EmailCampaignRequest
extends EmailCampaignBase
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents a single Email Campaign Request for the Email Campaign Service in Constant Contact.
    Always use this class when creating a request, and not the base one!
    The private inner fields are just the same as in EmailCampaignBase, but JSON annotations are different for the overwritten, hiding fields forbidden by the server.
    Author:
    ConstantContact
